<function>

access:   public

name: action

param: string, $spec

param: string, $text, NULL

return: string

</function>

Returns an action anchor, or just an action href.

* Parameters:

 * string //$spec//: The action specification.

 * string //$text//: A locale translation key.

* Returns string

Returns an action anchor, or just an action href.

If the $text link text is empty, will just return the
href value, not an <a href="">...</a> anchor tag.